data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath rambler in a quiet neighborhood. Backs up to walking path and city park. Room to grow in the partially finished basement. Fresh Paint in the majority of the main level. Updates include, leaf guard gutters installed 2018(lifetime warranty), Kitchen window, Bay window, and sliding glass door replaced 2018, Dinning room, bedrooms, and master bath windows all replaced 2021, Drive way and back patio paved 2022, New vinyl fence installed with 10-year warranty 2022, Master bath remodeled 2019. Full bath remodeled 2021, New water-resistant vinyl laminate flooring throughout main floor, Kitchen remodeled, new appliances and blue pearl granite countertops installed 2019, Storm door 2022, Smart Garage Door Opener 2022, Water Softener(owned)2019, Roof was replaced 2015, Furnace new in 2017, Updated light fixtures to include fans in all bedrooms, and smart fan in basement office. Front door Smart lock(will be replaced with new standard lock).
